ste.", "tokens": [51732, 286, 994, 380, 528, 264, 14770, 281, 352, 281, 5964, 13, 51814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13175810345951816, "compression_ratio": 1.8793103448275863, "no_speech_prob": 0.001977271633222699}, {"id": 19, "seek": 5848, "start": 58.68, "end": 61.879999999999995, "text": " So I ended up making my own cinnamon sticks and some ground cinnamon.", "tokens": [50374, 407, 286, 4590, 493, 1455, 452, 1065, 22969, 12518, 293, 512, 2727, 22969, 13, 50534], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1317692862616645, "compression_ratio": 1.8557993730407523, "no_speech_prob": 0.0025887740775942802}, {"id": 20, "seek": 5848, "start": 62.08, "end": 65.36, "text": " To make the cookies, I started by adding some of our homemade ground cinnamon", "tokens": [50544, 1407, 652, 264, 13670, 11, 286, 1409, 538, 5127, 512, 295, 527, 23336, 2727, 22969, 50708], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1317692862616645, "compression_ratio": 1.8557993730407523, "no_speech_prob": 0.0025887740775942802}, {"id": 21, "seek": 5848, "start": 65.36, "end": 68.28, "text": " and our toasted coconut to the rest of our dry cookie ingredients.", "tokens": [50708, 293, 527, 48951, 13551, 281, 264, 1472, 295, 527, 4016, 14417, 6952, 13, 50854], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1317692862616645, "compression_ratio": 1.8557993730407523, "no_speech_prob": 0.0025887740775942802}, {"id": 22, "seek": 5848, "start": 68.47999999999999, "end": 71.44, "text": " Then we can go ahead and give this a good stir and set it to the side", "tokens": [50864, 1396, 321, 393, 352, 2286, 293, 976, 341, 257, 665, 8946, 293, 992, 309, 281, 264, 1252, 51012], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1317692862616645, "compression_ratio": 1.8557993730407523, "no_speech_prob": 0.0025887740775942802}, {"id": 23, "seek": 5848, "start": 71.44, "end": 73.44, "text": " while we work on the rest of our wet ingredients.", "tokens": [51012, 1339, 321, 589, 322, 264, 1472, 295, 527, 6630, 6952, 13, 51112], "temper